{"tid":2186701,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全城護蘋壯黃圈「冇工開都登廣告」","createTime":"2020-09-03T06:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T06:47:04.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"598211c3db3a3f6ad2b62b8bd3dcddf9e126d62f","tid":2186701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:47:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/6NT5LE3AMBGSVJXLJRAR3M2III/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F6NT5LE3AMBGSVJXLJRAR3M2III%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVGN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=e6a3ba96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2F6NT5LE3AMBGSVJXLJRAR3M2III%2F&h=4a94a08d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/6NT5LE3AMBGSVJXLJRAR3M2III/</a><br />\n<br />\n全城護蘋壯黃圈「冇工開都登廣告」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wkqyHHBo-fKdZKdTRP0ziHeX6_A=/4151x3704/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K77JIXLK3ZGE7HI7YJIHW2PQGI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwkqyHHBo-fKdZKdTRP0ziHeX6_A%3D%2F4151x3704%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK77JIXLK3ZGE7HI7YJIHW2PQGI.jpg&h=d8bbd5e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【眾志成城】8月10日，200名警察踩入蘋果日報大樓搜查一幕場面震撼國際，不少人擔心《蘋果日報》翌日未能出版，甚至稱就算只出版「白紙」都照買斷。《蘋果》上下緊守崗位如常出版報紙，各界旋即開始登廣告「懲罰」，本來此舉為推廣業務，但今次意義超越商業考慮，有商戶明明經營艱難都要撐《蘋果》和表態。政府抗疫不力，多個行業早陷水深火熱，支持《蘋果》卻帶來意外效益，除結合黃色經濟圈，更成為一場由捍衞新聞自由演變的自救行動。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：分類廣告重生 創意搶眼球"}]}